radiographic_examinations.findings: Nondisplaced subcapital fracture on the medial side of both femoral necks and stage-I osteonecrosis of both femoral heads.
No evidence of displacement of the fractures.
radiographic_examinations.changes_over_time: At two years follow-up, showed no evidence of stress fractures in the femoral necks or progression of the osteonecrosis.

radiographic_examinations.findings: No evidence of osteonecrosis of the femoral heads or of fractures.
